    • Uses of BidirectionalIterable in net.markenwerk.commons.iterables

      Subinterfaces of BidirectionalIterable in net.markenwerk.commons.iterables 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      interface  ProtectedBidirectionalIterable<Payload>
      A ProtectedBidirectionalIterable is a BidirectionalIterable that guarantees that every call to Iterable.iterator() yields a ProtectedBidirectionalIterator.
